546
00:26:17,319 --> 00:26:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, ajmo dalje.

547
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:21,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je scenarij kada vi tražite druge osobe.

548
00:26:21,299 --> 00:26:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo sada vidjeti kako biste mogli koristiti tražilicu.

549
00:26:25,119 --> 00:26:27,819
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kada ne znate koga tražite,

550
00:26:27,819 --> 00:26:29,400
