669
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala za komentare.

670
00:32:54,119 --> 00:32:58,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, imate i drugu stranu, dakle povezivanje

671
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:59,720
