677
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] To je osobna odluka.

678
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] Isto stvar vijedi na LinkedInu.

679
00:33:15,559 --> 00:33:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vi uopće ne morate prihvaćati pozive ljudi

680
00:33:18,599 --> 00:33:21,119
